HEADWORD: Lampern
<hw>Lam"pern</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Lamprey</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>The river lamprey
(<spn>Ammoc⟦oe⟧tes fluviatilis</spn> syn. <spn>Lampetra
fluviatilis</spn>).</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><note>⟦hand⟧ The name is also applied to other river
